What is Declarative Pipeline:
-----------------------------
     - a structured way to write jenkins pipeline scripts
     - easier and more readable than scripted pipeline
     Uses predefined blocks like:
        pipline
        agent
        stages
        steps

    Basic systax structure:
    ------------------------
    pipeline {
        agent any

        stages{
            stage('Stage Name') {
                steps {
                    // commands
                }
            }
        }
    }



























